WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Hello, today our guests will each introduce an important person from their countries,

00:08.000 --> 00:15.600
and we'll discuss why they are famous. Confucius was a great teacher and thinker in

00:15.600 --> 00:25.400
ancient China. He lived over 2,000 years ago, and he is well known in many countries.

00:25.400 --> 00:33.400
William Shakespeare was English and wrote plays and poems. Although he died about 400 years ago,

00:33.400 --> 00:40.400
his plays are still seen and his poems are still read by many people.

00:40.400 --> 00:49.400
Mark Twain was an American writer. His works are studied in schools. His stories are set in the south of the US

00:49.400 --> 00:55.400
over 100 years ago, and readers still enjoy them very much.

